[style name="Text"]
Welcome to this new world!
Today will be a perfect day to begin your beautiful adventure.
Before we start, let’s learn the basic controls!
First, try moving to the left.
Press A to move left.
Great job! You did it.
Now try moving to the right.
Press D to move right.
Excellent!
You can also move upward using W  
and downward using S.  
Try pressing W to move up.
Nice!  
Now press S to move down.
Next is jumping.  
Press SPACE to jump!
Awesome! You learn fast.
Now let's practice combat:  
Press C to perform a melee attack.
Good!
You can also throw your weapon.  
Press V to throw it.
Great!
If you have multiple items, you can switch between them with G.  
Press G to switch items.
Nice!
You can open your inventory at any time using the O key.  
Press O to open the inventory.
Finally, to interact with objects —  
such as chests, NPCs, or signs —  
press E.
Perfect! Now you know all the basic controls.
Let’s move forward and begin the real adventure!